<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Blog App | Home</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Manrope:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/base.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/home.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="page-shell">
      <header class="topbar">
        <a href="/" class="brand">Inkspire</a>
        <nav class="topbar-links">
          <a href="/">Home</a>
          <a href="/compose">Compose</a>
          <a href="/blog">Blogs</a>
        </nav>
      </header>

      <main class="hero-grid">
        <section class="hero-copy card">
          <span class="eyebrow">Simple publishing space</span>
          <h1>Write, organize, and share stories that feel worth reading.</h1>
          <p>
            A clean blog dashboard for creators who want fewer distractions and
            more room for ideas. Start drafting, sort content by category, and
            keep your writing flow steady.
          </p>

          <div class="hero-actions">
            <a href="/compose" class="button primary">Start Writing</a>
            <a href="/blog" class="button secondary">Explore Posts</a>
          </div>

          <div class="stats-row">
            <article>
              <strong>120+</strong>
              <span>Stories drafted</span>
            </article>
            <article>
              <strong>8</strong>
              <span>Popular categories</span>
            </article>
            <article>
              <strong>24/7</strong>
              <span>Creative momentum</span>
            </article>
          </div>
        </section>

        <aside class="hero-panel card">
          <div class="panel-heading">
            <span class="panel-tag">Featured Spaces</span>
            <h2>What readers can discover</h2>
          </div>

          <div class="option-list">
            <article class="option-card">
              <h3>Technology</h3>
              <p>Thoughts on software, AI, apps, and the web.</p>
            </article>
            <article class="option-card">
              <h3>Lifestyle</h3>
              <p>Daily routines, habits, wellness, and productivity ideas.</p>
            </article>
            <article class="option-card">
              <h3>Travel</h3>
              <p>Memories, guides, and places worth bookmarking.</p>
            </article>
            <article class="option-card">
              <h3>Personal Notes</h3>
              <p>Short reflections, lessons, and behind-the-scenes writing.</p>
            </article>
          </div>
        </aside>
      </main>

      <section class="highlights">
        <article class="highlight card">
          <span>Fast drafting</span>
          <h3>Compose posts with a minimal workflow</h3>
          <p>
            Focus on title, description, and category first. Keep the writing
            experience lightweight and easy to maintain.
          </p>
        </article>
        <article class="highlight card">
          <span>Clean browsing</span>
          <h3>Showcase blogs in a modern card layout</h3>
          <p>
            Give readers an organized page where they can scan categories and
            discover fresh content quickly.
          </p>
        </article>
        <article class="highlight card">
          <span>Simple structure</span>
          <h3>Perfect for an early-stage CRUD blog app</h3>
          <p>
            The layout is intentionally basic, polished, and easy to connect to
            your routes and database later.
          </p>
        </article>
      </section>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
